descriptionHtml:
Browse and play your music by albums, artists, genres, songs, playlists, folders, and album artists.

Music Player lets you manage all your audio files and play the music file quickly and easily. You may easily browse and play music songs and create your playlist.

Audio Player for All Type of Audio Formats
Music Player supports all music and audio formats including MP3, MIDI, WAV, FLAC, AAC, APE, etc

Equalizer with great sound-
This MP3 player with bass boost, reverb effects, etc, the built-in equalizer will enhance your music listening experience.

Key Features :
● Support with Wearable Device. Easy to access music player from wearable devices.
● Support all music and audio formats, like MP3, MIDI, WAV, FLAC, AAC, APE, etc.
● Play songs in shuffle, order or loop
● Browse and play your music by playlists, songs, artists, albums, folders, and album artists.
● Show recent playlist and most top songs playlist
● Offline music player, songs player, audio player, mp3 player with high quality.
● Play songs in shuffle, order or loop
● Notification STATUS support: display album artwork, title, and artist, play/pause, skip forward and stop CONTROLS in notification status.
● Powerful equalizer with bass boost, reverb effects, etc.
● Set music as a ringtone for your choice, or you can change it.
● Sleep Timer
● Headset support. Support one button and multiple buttons headsets. Leave your device in the pocket!
● Music Library wide SEARCH.
● Custom Playlist, set albums, artists, genres, folders songs to playlist, show recent playlist
● Equalizer enables with virtualizer and Bass boost feature.
● Search interface to get favorite songs
● Settings to control Headset settings
● Video and Audio songs in single android application and Video player with popup window player, PIP mode, Subtitle, dual audio support sleep timer and Playback speedetc.

🎵 Free Music Player for Android Phones 🎵 - This is a powerful and high-quality mp3 player and video player app which supports all formats of audio files and video files. You can locate and manage all music and audio files from your phone memory and SD card. 👉 You can use this free offline Music Player as your default mp3 player and default video player. It’s a HQ audio player and HD Video player where you can play Full HD, 4K, and 8K videos using this app. You can identify all your mp3 audio files and videos files on your Android device and SD card automatically.


⭐ MP3 Player Supported Formats ⭐
This Audio Player supports all types of audio formats like MP3, MIDI, WAV, FLAC, AAC, APE, OGC, etc.


⭐ Video Player Supported Formats ⭐
This offline Media Player plays almost all HQ video formats like 8K, 4K, Mp4, AVI, M4V, FLV, MKV, TS, MPG, 3GP, etc.


⭐ Powerful Equalizer and Bass Booster ⭐
This free offline MP3 Player app has a Powerful Equalizer and Bass boosters with presets like Rock, Pop, Jazz, Flat, Normal, Dance, Folk, Classical, Heavy Metal, Reverb effects, the built-in equalizer will enhance your music listening experience.


⭐ High-Quality Music & Video Player ⭐
This is an HQ MP3 and Media Player which will let you play music and video with high quality and clarity. It has professional-level Audio and Video codecs to play high-quality content on your device.


⭐ Free Live AM & FM Radio ⭐
This Audio Player supports you to listen to more than 200+ Countries' live Internet Radio Stations around the world for free. You can fetch specific language-specific FM Radio Stations.


⭐ Listen to the best music with a customizable player ⭐
What makes the music app unique is that you can use it offline and fully customize your experience. We want to make it easy for you, and that’s why we have a great no WIFI Music app that you can enjoy on the spot. On top of that, our free audio app has everything you need from a media player and so much more. You can view the album, artist, track, and genre directly from the interface. we added the opportunity to play videos from the YouTube Music trending video system and videos can be played via the floating player if you want.


Additional Features:
🌟 Very comprehensive, customizable free music app.

🌟 It has a Powerful Equalizer with Super Bass Booster

🌟 Shake your phone to Play or Pause, Play Next Song or Previous Song
🌟 Search by songs, artist, playlist, and album, etc.
🌟 Support Bluetooth/Headset controls one button or multiple buttons headsets.
🌟 The best offline music player app for free. no wifi is required to play the music.
🌟 This is the best alternative for a default music app.
🌟 Listen to radio stations from over 200 countries.
